<p class=3D"bull-s"><a id=3D"page_106"></a><span class=3D"bul-s">=E2=80=A2<=
/span> It involves baselining requirements after sign-off, where appropriat=
e, responding to change, and keeping the requirements maintained and up to =
date.</p>
<p class=3D"bull-s"><span class=3D"bul-s">=E2=80=A2</span> The specific req=
